# Project showcase images
#
# Drop carousel images here, matching the filenames declared in
# `src/data/projects.js` under each entry's `images` array. Currently
# expected:
#
#   sofia-married-1.jpg, sofia-married-2.jpg, sofia-married-3.jpg
#   veyra-organization-1.jpg, veyra-organization-2.jpg
#   zeronet-labs-1.jpg, zeronet-labs-2.jpg
#
# Any of jpg / jpeg / png / webp / avif are valid; the carousel inlines
# them via `import.meta.glob` so the file extension is preserved in the
# final asset URL.
